Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在坚定无比的内心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.08,0:00:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远以最强的节奏揭开案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.92,0:00:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的舞台是市中心的旅馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独特的屋子全都是谜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀古饭店的神秘事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.14,0:01:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京单轨电车 一番町站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.74,0:01:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.64,0:01:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车票给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实爸爸可以跟我们一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.48,0:01:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豚乐园玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堂堂一个男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看海豚像什么话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.05,0:02:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人梦想的天堂还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是赛马会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.49,0:02:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次要是让我下对马的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上就请你们吃豪华晚餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.20,0:02:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我们家的财政出现赤字就谢天谢地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.67,0:02:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 直美她怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.01,0:02:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫我们快点去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.58,0:02:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时看到两个美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气还真是不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您该不会是毛利小五郎先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.32,0:02:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位名侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.06,0:02:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天运气真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的侦探迷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等佳央理 你太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不失礼 千万别这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算去海豚乐园玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道毛利先生要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去海豚乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海豚乐园隔壁的赛马会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不知道我们一路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.42,0:03:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是能跟你同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.82,0:03:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们还在等一位朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳央理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一个大美人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来得真早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.94,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要搭1:20的电车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还有10分钟嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.51,0:03:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位先生是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是名侦探毛利小五郎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是碰巧遇到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个是大学时的同班同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.76,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个星期我们办了一次同学会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们有个朋友一直在国外工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时没有来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她有点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天突然回国了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人开一次小型的聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来还能看到一位美女啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当年她可是我们四个人中间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最受男生欢迎的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.51,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿 她在哪儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.32,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在就住在海豚公园的饭店里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些年来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直住在国外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从事童装设计的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.16,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是设计师和杂志编辑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.40,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几位都可以说是才貌兼备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您太抬举我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个就别客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.91,0:04:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 你这次不是要独立门户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创立一家你自己的工作室吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有我是个最没用的家族主妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我们几个都先结婚生子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福得不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛 就知道嘲笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开往海豚乐园的电车即将进站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位旅客站在安全线外候车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.07,0:05:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看另外一位大美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上电车 上电车 快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.49,0:05:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京单轨电车 海豚乐园站前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是海豚乐园的饭店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这家饭店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上个月才隆重开张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到饭店里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装潢得这么古典啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这里就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.51,0:05:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭店里所谓的“怀古楼层”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“怀古楼层”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是将这家饭店建造之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原有那家老饭店的风情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这里表现出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家随我到直美的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美到底住在几号房啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得她住的是503号房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,503房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.17,0:06:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算赶上了 刚好两点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美在搞什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打电话叫我们早点来自己却在睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿她没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美 直美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像没有把门锁上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美 我们进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才第一次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.80,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.85,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌 先冷静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不要碰屋里面的任何东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.23,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫你不要乱碰东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视应该是自动切断的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是台投币式电视机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.64,0:07:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰 总而言之先去报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先见到尸体的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们三位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.88,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有每次都碰巧在场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.89,0:07:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利君是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.09,0:07:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待搜证之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须录取三位的口供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能请三位在此稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来做她们的保镖怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看没这个必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 千叶君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.94,0:07:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来接待这三位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毛利君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何 高木君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.46,0:08:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者叫藤村直美 27岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说目前是在国外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从事童装设计工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在被害人的裙子口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到这样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用来防范色狼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女用催泪瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 催泪瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位藤村小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是因为长年居住在国外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会特别小心谨慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间怎么会有这么老旧的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才听说这里叫怀古套房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呈现出来的都是过去旧饭店的摆设
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会放了台投币式的电视机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台电视机的设计是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞入100元后可以看一小时的电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们在进入这个房间后不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视就自动关闭了对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 当时大约是下午两点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据摆在电视机上的说明来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.05,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100元的硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次似乎只能塞一个进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.75,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视打开的时间是在一点左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡时间是在什么时侯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计是在正午到下午一点之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 她是在打开电视之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就遭到凶手的攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你看这些零食好有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.40,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有看过这样的零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你这小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.94,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柠檬汽水糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放长线软糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四角糖和味增鲜贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些全是我以前吃过的零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.72,0:09:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些点心据我所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是饭店特别准备给房客作茶点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.39,0:09:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是凶手跟被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在争执的时候把东西弄乱的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还有一根雪糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过融化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想被害人一定是准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边吃雪糕边看电视的时候遇害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个人现在去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.48,0:10:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱里面是不是还有雪糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.48,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 里面还有好几根雪糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些雪糕也满叫人怀念的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来毛利君说的一定错不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.76,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.19,0:10:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种雪糕根本不是过去的品牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被害人自己买来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.90,0:10:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 上面有点水渍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 你看这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有点湿湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.24,0:10:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看八成是被花瓶里的水给洒到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你在下午一点之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经把洗好的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到这个客房是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过我当时看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门上挂着那张“请勿打搅”的牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那时我没有进去房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么当时的房门有没有上锁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼 又想捣蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.10,0:11:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说 门有上锁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有去碰那个门把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.91,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在桌子下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了被害人的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.88,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能查查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她曾经给什么人打过电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.09,0:11:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.12,0:11:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刚才三位小姐其中的一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.77,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者曾在下午1:08打过这个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道打完之后没多久就死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本小姐接到这个电话不久以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟我们交谈起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 直美的确是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我们要快点过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话显示是1:08
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时侯请问你在什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都在单轨电车的一番町站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个从一点以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.43,0:12:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈美晚了10 分钟才到车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们三个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟毛利先生一起上了1:20 的电车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.38,0:12:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到这家饭店的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在1:50左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走到直美房间的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是下午两点整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 她们三位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在命案发生当时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.69,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有充分的不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后那个能不能请三位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回到现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对发现尸体前后的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一次详细的叙述
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.10,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.84,0:12:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对是一次计划性的谋杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的推理没有错的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手应该就是她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜我还没有证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.25,0:13:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么有塑料袋摩擦的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人经过了巧妙计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.22,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位今天的调查到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可以离开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这样吧 目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.67,0:13:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来送她们…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.38,0:13:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然很想送她们回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.65,0:13:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过目前的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然不允许我这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得说这显然是一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.52,0:13:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过巧妙计划的谋杀案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且杀人凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是目前在场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.86,0:13:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三位小姐的其中一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我们之中有一个是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么每次都是这句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.17,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是藤村小姐的那瓶催泪瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.38,0:14:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明把它放在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以没有拿出来用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最有可能的说法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这名凶手是她原本就认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是房间的钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把钥匙就放在桌上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这名凶手是个强盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会在行凶之后延长尸体的发现时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必定会在把房门锁上之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再逃离现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她们三位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.57,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有下午一点以后的不在场证明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实凶手真正的行凶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要比下午一点早了好几十分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.11,0:14:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依我判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手应该是在12:20 左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下罪行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话那台电视机又怎么解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视关闭的时间是两点以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.69,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样势必在一点钟过后塞进硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 凶手就算不在现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一样可以把硬币塞进投币口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.69,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她只要利用散落在地上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些零食就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心几时也看起电视来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是利用这些来完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.27,0:15:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑上放长线软糖就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看了就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把放长线软糖的线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.09,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂在电视机旁边的投币口上方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把这根雪糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆在电视转台器和柜子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是架桥一样腾空放着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把这个软糖拉过来的线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压到这根雪糕的下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有100元硬币吗 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.41,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把它放进投币口试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有线挡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬币没有办法顺利进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手就是做了这个手法之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.98,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才离开现场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间一久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.32,0:15:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪糕就自然会融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到雪糕融化之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一失去支撑就会往下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说电视机前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以会掉了一地的零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了掩饰凶手的这种手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转台器的旋转扭和旁边的拒子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.11,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以会有水渍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是曾经摆放雪糕留下的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.38,0:16:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上那支雪糕是最近才上市的雪糕品种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.35,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是饭店事先留在冰箱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.22,0:16:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为房客准备的冷饮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是直美自己买来吃的也不一定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.69,0:16:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手之所以没有把门锁上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也同样是为了这个手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她把门给锁上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时侯跟朋友到了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法立刻进入房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来就没有办法看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视关闭的那个瞬间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果凶手没有让人看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视消失的瞬间就没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那门把上的那个牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是谁挂的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该也是凶手挂上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这之间只有短短的一小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手离开现场后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个套房等于是处在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都能进入的状态下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一有什么人进来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的计划就完全泡汤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.67,0:17:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在1:08的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还曾经接到直美打给我的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.81,0:17:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美要是在一点之前就被凶手杀害的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能打那通电话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也对啊 毛利君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的通话记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和收信息记录都是吻合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是凶手利用死者的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行凶之后打出去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.89,0:17:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是公仁子和直美明明说话了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.53,0:17:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 她们根本不可能在交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这名凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本公仁子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这个地方行凶之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就带着藤村直美小姐的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接回到了一番町车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先和佳央理小姐会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.69,0:18:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来到了一点钟左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就利用你放在口袋里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤村小姐的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了个电话里给你自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后装出你和藤村小姐交谈的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要趁着大家发现尸体后的慌乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手机放回房里就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说有证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想证据应该还在你的身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据就是你外套口袋里的那个塑料袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.68,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有塑料袋难道不可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是把藤村小姐的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到里面之后才带出去的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须请你配合我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.94,0:19:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查一下你的口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.07,0:19:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就试着把它放到灯光下看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.38,0:19:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面粘了好几个指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以很明显的看出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好几个直立的指纹的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我在看到你的手机号码的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就发现了一个非常有趣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.43,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,02058252805
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把手机按键的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿来参考一下就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人打电话给你的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会用到正中间的这几个按钮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个塑料袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘到的这几个直立的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你隔着那个塑料袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下自己手机号码的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.62,0:19:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把死者的手机拿过来看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.82,0:19:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个塑料袋既然一直放在我的口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有我的指纹有什么好奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是死看的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置刚好吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有办法原谅直美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样 公仁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚从大学毕业的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩最优秀的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.33,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以被推荐到国外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为知名的服装厂商工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美得到了这项殊荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的在国外成为知名童装设计师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这份殊荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是属于我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.14,0:20:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道直美却跑去巴结教授
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是开第二届同学会的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授因为喝醉了说出真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远也不会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不是也要独立门户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立自己的工作室吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全是我骗你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我才被公司裁员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我犯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生中唯一一次错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.90,0:21:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.74,0:21:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我就必须遭到这样的命运呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天之所以会有这么悲惨的下场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是直美间接害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当年她把我的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.81,0:21:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统统夺走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.95,0:21:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.08,0:21:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到还有夜间演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
